personalInfo.clubAffl: Soaring Eagles GC (Horseheads, New York); Emerald Dunes Club (West Palm Beach, Florida)

tourBios.exmtStatus: Conditional - Additional Qualifying Tournament Finisher or Finished 76-100 on 2014 Web.com Tour Money List
tourBios.carHigh:
2014: Finished T71 at Web.com Tour Q-School in December...In lone Tour start, missed the cut at the Nova Scotia Open in July...Made eight PGA TOUR Canada appearances, recording three cuts made. Best finish was a T25 at The Syncrude Boreal in June.

2013: Missed the cut in his only start on PGA TOUR Canada, at the Cape Breton Classic...Finished T73 in December's Web.com Tour Q-School.
tourBios.otherCarHigh: Two time all-state and three-time conference Player of the Year at Horseheads High School in New York...Two-time Academic All-Big 10 at Ohio State University.
tourBios.personal: Father, Joey, won seven PGA TOUR events and is a current Champions Tour player...Favorite golf memory is winning the Father/Son Golf Tournament at Disney World and beating his dad in golf for the first time...If he were not a professional golfer would be a golf course architect or a fishing guide...Never travels without his insulin pump...Superstition leads him to only using a New York, Ohio or 1990 quarter as a ball marker...Is a country music fan and enjoys barbecue...Follows Ohio State football and Syracuse basketball along with the New York Mets and Buffalo Bills...Enjoys watching "Duck Dynasty" and Red Arrow TV...Dream golf foursome would include his brother Ryan, his dad and his uncle Mike Hulbert (also a PGA TOUR winner)...Not many people know he has type-1 diabetes...Winning on the PGA TOUR is on his bucket list along with having a family and driving a NASCAR stock car...Twitter account is @jsindelar67.
